				<p sameAs="title">Private letter from Fernão Dias, clergyman, to Mateus Pereira, a secretary of the Holy Office</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author reports an incorrect theological behaviour and asks for advice</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">The header and body of the letter contain information that allows us to conclude this is an accusation, motivated by the statements made  by the prior of Santa Maria, Gaspar Barreto, during a public event.</p>
